      "content": "thanks. this is a good start, it's pretty readable. \n\ni just ran it through the tool though and the score is actually kind of low—it's only hitting around a 10. for a professional handbook, we really want that score to be higher so it feels more \"active\" and \"energetic\" to the new employees. \n\ncould you try a second draft? please keep it professional and don't make it messy, but try to bump that verb count up significantly. just make sure the instructions stay clear and useful.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
